OL,5, Marks & Spencer has stopped selling    
OL,6, disposable barbecues in its stores     
OL,7, across the UK.                         
OL,9,FAnnouncing the move, the supermarket   
OL,10,Fsaid it wanted "to help protect open   
OL,11,Fspaces and reduce the risk of fires".  
OL,13,FLondon Fire Brigade, which has been    
OL,14,Fcalling for a ban on the sale of       
OL,15,Fdisposable barbecues, welcomed the     
OL,16,Fmove, saying it was "good news".       
OL,18,FIt comes after the UK experienced its  
OL,19,Fhottest day ever on record, with 40C   
OL,20,Fexceeded for the first time.           
